700900f-a.title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Hering Avenue
700900f-a.text:
East Gunhill Road, south side, east from Hering Ave. The letter
boxes are in front of No. 1164, and the 1-story frame real estate office
is No. 1170 at the S.W. corner of Tenbroeck Ave.
June 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
